nnoremap <silent> <Leader>n :NERDTreeToggle \| NERDTreeMirror<CR>
nnoremap <Leader>N :NERDTreeMirror \| NERDTreeFocus \| wincmd p \| NERDTreeFind<CR>

" [b and ]b for prev/next buffer
